title: LF Ranked 5's team
body:
Currently I'm a jungle/mid player in plat 5 looking to get a ranked 5's team going. Looking for people gold+ just to try keep it relatively competitive.

Message me either here or on the client with your IGN, Preferred Lane and Rank. It'd preferable if you have the use of discord for shotcalling etc. as well

My IGN: Vanilla Bear
